---
title: Mojo-Inspired Pork Chops with Cilantro-Citrus Sauce
description: This pork chop bowl is inspired by the bright flavours of Cuba. Orange, lime, cilantro and jalapeño play double-duty in a zesty drizzly sauce and as a flavourful marinade. Got a couple of hours before you want to eat dinner? Marinate the pork to soak up extra flavour.

